<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Web Page</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .wrapper {
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .sidebar {
            width: 100px;
            background-color: #ccc;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: black;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 100px; 
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: orange;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: darkorange;
        }

        .info-box {
            background-color: orange;
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid blue;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 60%;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="sidebar"></div> 

    <div class="content">
        <h1>My Web Page</h1>

        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="/catalog" class="btn">Catalog</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn">Contact</a>
			<a href="/gallery" class="btn">Gallery</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <p>Welcome to my website prototype! Here, you'll find the perfect computer for your needs, whether it's for work, gaming, or as a gift.  
            Our selection covers everything from high-performance gaming rigs to budget-friendly office machines.  
            We aim to make choosing the right computer easy, convenient, and hassle-free.  
            Browse through our catalog, compare specifications, and find the perfect match.  
            Our platform is designed to help you make an informed decision with detailed descriptions, user reviews, and expert recommendations.  
            No matter your budget or technical expertise, we're here to guide you to the best choice!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sidebar"></div> 
</div>

</body>
</html>
